  "ai_usage": "Use to make headings responsive WITHOUT media queries. Pattern: font-size: clamp(MIN, REM + VW, MAX). ALWAYS include a rem term in the middle (e.g. 1rem + 4vw) so the text still scales with user zoom — a pure vw value is an accessibility failure. Pick MIN/MAX from your type scale. Resize the catalog frame / window to see it interpolate.",
